events.name: 話しかける並列・自動実行

parameters:
Clea: Do you happen to know a place around here where we
can find the herb called Imiserinosu's Lips?

Bar Owner: Oh, alchemy, huh? The Overflowing Blossom Cave
is a treasure trove of medicinal herbs.
Mage Relm: Please mark it on the map. Let's go!

\CL Area Unlocked\c[18]\CL Oros Region/Overflowing Blossom
Cave\c[0]
Thief Nora: ...Huh!? S-Sorry, was I being too loud?

One-armed old man: Stop right there, there might be a
goblin nest nearby.

Mage Relm: I refuse! These girls are members of the
adventurer guild that I hired.

Mage Relm: Goblins are nothing, a piece of cake for me! I'm
a genius from the Magic Academy, so I've got this under
control!
One-armed old man: ...I did give you a warning.

Mage Relm: Hmph, let's go! The time of a genius is more
precious than anything else, after all.

Clea: Thank you for your advice. However, it is my job to
complete the request.

Bar Owner: Ah, did she go? Is everything alright, Opro's
husband?

One-armed Opro: Even if you're adventurers, you should be
able to escape from goblins, right?

One-armed Opro: Well, I'm going to the mountains for an
investigation too. The goblins might be attracted to the
scent of these women.
Innkeeper: Have you found what you were looking for?
Clea: I found it, but I was interrupted by goblins.
Clea: Is the old man from earlier here?

Innkeeper: Haha, it's quite impressive that you understand
the abilities of Oplo's husband.

Innkeeper: I'll pass on the message about the goblins to
you.

Mage Relm: But then we won't know when we can get the
medicinal herbs!
Innkeeper: Here, the medicinal herbs you were looking for.
Mage Relm: Um, how much are you planning to sell it for!?

Innkeeper: It's an exchange of information, and this is a
bonus! It's convenient for me because I was looking for the
whereabouts of the goblins.
Mage Relm: In that case, the negotiation is complete!

Innkeeper: He's someone who lives as what you would call a
specialist in goblins and orcs, commonly known as a hunter.
Innkeeper: In that field, he's famous as a Goblin Slayer.

Mage Relm: Since we've accomplished our objective, let's go
back! Now, please take us to the Adventurer's Guild.
Clea: Isn't this the Magic Academy?
Mage Relm: Yes, I have a little errand to take care of.
One-armed old man: Is there something you need from me?

As an adventurer, selling medicinal herbs at a high price
is the perfect way for someone like me to earn some pocket
money.
Innkeeper: I recommend our medicinal cuisine!

Drunk customer: Delicious wine, delicious cheese, there's
nothing more I could wish for in life.

Forest Guide: I make a profit by guiding alchemists through
the forest.
